   "source": [
    "import admix\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import matplotlib as mpl\n",
    "import os"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "978c9fc0-da59-4fd3-9e38-ab7340e62d81",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "REF_PFILE = \"/u/project/pasaniuc/kangchen/DATA/plink2-1kg/out/pgen/build38\"\n",
    "PCA_DIR = \"\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "aff206be-b816-4c66-9ea5-5f54a804fd20",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df_plot = (\n",
    "    pd.read_csv(os.path.join(PCA_DIR, \"pca.eigenvec\"), delim_whitespace=True)\n",
    "    .set_index(\"IID\")\n",
    "    .drop(columns=[\"#FID\"])\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "with open(os.path.join(PCA_DIR, \"pca.eigenval\")) as f:\n",
    "    eigenval = np.array([float(l.strip()) for l in f.readlines()])\n",
    "    varexp = eigenval / eigenval.sum()\n",
    "df_pop = pd.read_csv(REF_PFILE + \".psam\", delim_whitespace=True, index_col=0)\n",
    "\n",
    "df_plot[\"SUPERPOP\"] = df_pop[\"SuperPop\"].reindex(df_plot.index)\n",
    "df_plot[\"POP\"] = df_pop[\"Population\"].reindex(df_plot.index)\n",
    "df_plot[\"SUPERPOP\"] = df_plot[\"SUPERPOP\"].fillna(\"MEX\")\n",
    "df_plot[\"POP\"] = df_plot[\"POP\"].fillna(\"MEX\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# reorder MEX to the bottom of the data frame\n",
    "df_plot = pd.concat([df_plot[df_plot.POP != \"MEX\"], df_plot[df_plot.POP == \"MEX\"]])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "9d3157c9-0de0-44be-aa5b-e0f58330a722",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1200x600 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "df_plot = df_plot[df_plot.SUPERPOP.isin([\"MEX\", \"AFR\"])]\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(figsize=(8, 4), dpi=150, ncols=2)\n",
    "admix.plot.pca(\n",
    "    df_plot[df_plot.POP != \"MEX\"],\n",
    "    x=\"PC1\",\n",
    "    y=\"PC2\",\n",
    "    label_col=\"POP\",\n",
    "    alpha={\"MEX\": 0.1},\n",
    "    ax=axes[0],\n",
    ")\n",
    "axes[0].set_xlabel(f\"PC1 ({varexp[0] * 100:.2g}%)\")\n",
    "axes[0].set_ylabel(f\"PC2 ({varexp[1] * 100:.2g}%)\")\n",
    "\n",
    "admix.plot.pca(\n",
    "    df_plot, x=\"PC1\", y=\"PC2\", label_col=\"POP\", alpha={\"MEX\": 0.1}, ax=axes[1]\n",
    ")\n",
    "axes[1].set_xlabel(f\"PC1 ({varexp[0] * 100:.2g}%)\")\n",
    "axes[1].set_ylabel(f\"PC2 ({varexp[1] * 100:.2g}%)\")\n",
    "fig.tight_layout()"
   ]
  },
